column2: Mostly sunny- winds calm- temp 67- common loon- eastern kingbird- kingfisher.  The shoreline vegitation appears to be lagging in winter recovery- still considerable brown/downed cattails.
pair of common loons within sight of testing site.  Temp 86 f humidity 80% with storm approaching from the west.  40% cloud cover at sampling time.
